{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are a Horse. You play as a wild horse with a freeform camera. It is you versus the world avoiding being captured. Natural disasters involving the elements, man, and gravity are your enemy. Preserve and increase your herd through your offspring, extending your lineage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328040/extras/Horse_and_his_Herd_escapes_from_the_enemy_Wranglers.gif?t=1736779397\" /><br> <br>You have no weapons, no rider, and a limited to no onscreen user interface.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328040/extras/Horse_Herd_flipping_over_enemy_Wrangler_Trucks_at_the_Lake.gif?t=1736779397\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From a casual play mode for simply exploring to your heart's content to a full-blown single-player story mode that digs deep into this world with possible sinister intentions.\u00a0It is up to you how you want to play and fantastically evolve!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328040/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736779397","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328040/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736779397","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328040/3f55d888a76143fa79898440780980ab1d4b7ec4/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736779397","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328040/3f55d888a76143fa79898440780980ab1d4b7ec4/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736779397","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are